            "text": "{\"code\":0,\"message\":\"OK\",\"data\":{\"count\":1,\"documents\":[{\"body\":\"<div>Download the LINE Chrome extension.</div><div><br></div><div>LINE Chrome app service will end on March 8, 2018 as the Chrome Web Store no longer supports apps.&nbsp;</div><div>However, you can install a Chrome extension to continue using LINE.</div><div>Download the LINE Chrome extension now by clicking the Download button below.</div><div><br></div><div><div><a href=\\\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/line/ophjlpahpchlmihnnnihgmmeilfjmjjc\\\">Download LINE extension</a></div><div>&nbsp;</div><div>We apologize for any inconvenience. Thank you for your understanding and continued support of LINE.</div></div>\",\"open\":1516633200000,\"close\":253402268340000,\"title\":\"End of LINE Chrome app service\",\"sortOrder\":1516674216283,\"revision\":1290290,\"registered\":1516674216172,\"fmtRegistered\":\"Jan 23, 2018\",\"newBadge\":false,\"id\":20077916,\"updated\":1519797223700}]}}"
